{"id":105450,"date":"2018-07-12T11:00:56","date_gmt":"2018-07-12T15:00:56","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/techvibes.com\/?p=105450"},"modified":"2018-07-12T14:58:29","modified_gmt":"2018-07-12T18:58:29","slug":"killer-spaces-rl-solutions-toronto","status":"publish","type":"magazine","link":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/magazine\/killer-spaces-rl-solutions-toronto","title":{"rendered":"RL Solutions&#8217; Cozy Lakefront Lodge"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>At one point, <a href=\"http:\/\/www.rlsolutions.com\/home\" target=\"_blank\">RL Solutions<\/a>\u2019 software fit on three floppy disks. Things are a bit different now.<\/p>\n<p>The healthcare enterprise software company, founded in 1997 (back when floppy disks made sense) has expanded just a bit from those early days.\u00a0RL Solutions now works with over 2,000 clients around the world, including <a href=\"https:\/\/borndigital.com\/2018\/06\/01\/sickkids-hospital-is-going-completely-digital\" target=\"_blank\">SickKids<\/a> and Johns Hopkins. In some cases, they even work with entire countries, like Denmark.<\/p>\n<p>Sanjay Malaviya is the president and CEO of RL Solutions, and like all great business ideas, his story began when he ran into a problem he couldn&#8217;t solve through ordinary means. Malaviya worked at St. Michael\u2019s Hospital in Toronto and a colleague asked him if he could convert the existing paper-based patient feedback process into an easier-to-manage software solution.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106338\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-1.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-1\" width=\"1549\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-1.jpg 1549w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-1-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-1-1280x854.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1549px) 100vw, 1549px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>That favor for a colleague\u2014just over 20 years ago\u2014sprung RL Solutions\u00a0on a path to become the healthcare giant it is now. It wasn&#8217;t always glory and paydays in the beginning though, as Malaviya began the company with a single desk in a waterfront condo. Since then, thankfully things have gotten a\u00a0tad larger. The company now occupies over 41,000 square feet on floors 1 Yonge Street in Toronto, a historic waterfront building that\u00a0also serves as the headquarters of the Toronto Star.<\/p>\n<p>Today, RL Solutions provides their clients with risk management, patient feedback, infection prevention, peer reviews, claims management and a host of other services. They help healthcare organizations improve the quality of care\u2014a task they do not take lightly.<\/p>\n<p>Oh, and if you were wondering\u2014yes, Malaviya\u2019s old stomping ground of St. Michael&#8217;s Hospital is\u00a0indeed a client of RL Solutions.<\/p>\n<h3>Work<\/h3>\n<p>The current working space is reflective of years of input from RL Solutions staff over the years. It has a distinct emphasis on community and collaboration with different areas dedicated to eating, working and enjoying some off-time.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106312\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-27.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-27\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-27.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-27-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-27-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-27-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-27-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106336\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-3.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-3\" width=\"1549\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-3.jpg 1549w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-3-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-3-1280x854.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1549px) 100vw, 1549px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106324\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-15.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-15\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-15.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-15-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-15-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-15-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-15-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Every year, the team heads up to the Muskoka region for a company-wide retreat, and that love for the cottage country definitely followed RL Solutions home. There is a definite wood motif happening across the office, from gorgeous wooden floors to light and ceiling fixtures that add a rugged complexity to the streamlined workspaces.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106318\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-21.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-21\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-21.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-21-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-21-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-21-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-21-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>That theme continues with The Cabin, a way to bring the cottage back to downtown Toronto. The wooden features bring a sense of coziness to the surrounding outdoor concrete jungle. And no cottage is complete without some video games and musical instruments, and of course some oars and moose on the walls for good measure.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_106322\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-106322\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-106322 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-17-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-17\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-17-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-17-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-17-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-17-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-17.jpg 1550w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-106322\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Taking \u201ccottage in the city\u201d to heart.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-106332\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-