/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-16-1024x682.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-16\" width=\"1024\" height=\"682\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-16-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-16-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-16-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-16.jpg 1550w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>There are collaborative spaces spread across the three floors to host meetings or have quick chats. RL Solutions caters to every kind of worker, boasting quiet phone pods and booths and even some walking treadmill desks to keep the blood flowing through those active employees. Some of the teams you may find throughout the space include developers, marketing, finance and operations.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106311\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-28.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-28\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-28.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-28-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-28-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-28-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-28-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106335\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-4.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-4\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-4.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-4-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-4-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-4-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Each of the three floors boasts different themes when it comes to meeting and communal spaces. Floor 21 is inspired by sports, though you won&#8217;t find specific teams on the walls\u2014there\u2019s far too much passion for teams across the world to name drop anyone in particular. Floor 22 borrows names from Canadian natural landmarks like Boreal and the Maritimes, while floor 23 is inspired by Toronto, sporting familiar area code names like 416, 647 and 905.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106317\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-22.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-22\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-22.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-22-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-22-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-22-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-22-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>\u201cRL is built on a foundation of trust,\u201d said Mike Etzinger, VP of Marketing. \u201cThat\u2019s why we have flexible vacation, the pub, a ping pong stadium and a gym.&#8221;<\/p>\n<blockquote><p>&#8220;When we built our office, we wanted a space that reflected this feeling of trust while also encouraging an environment of collaboration and comradery.&#8221;<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<h3>Food<\/h3>\n<p>Keeping employees satiated and happy is something RL Solutions takes pride in. Breakfast is offered and rotated every morning, so you may find anything from bagels to parfaits to oatmeal waiting for you when you stroll in.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106327\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-12.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-12\" width=\"1549\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-12.jpg 1549w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-12-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-12-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-12-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-12-1280x854.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1549px) 100vw, 1549px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106326\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-13.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-13\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-13.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-13-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-13-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-13-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-13-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106325\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-14.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-14\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-14.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-14-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-14-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-14-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-14-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Snacks are strategically placed: breakfast is served on floor 23, but\u00a0quick eats like fresh fruit, chips and popcorn are housed on floors 22 and 21, encouraging colleagues to move between floors and interact with\u00a0one other if they want a mid-afternoon pick-me-up.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106316\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-23.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-23\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1035\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-23.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-23-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-23-768x513.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-23-1024x684.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-23-1280x855.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>Speaking of that mid-afternoon perk, coffee is no joke here. Eight machines help keep employees happy with drips and lattes galore, and if you\u2019re one of those \u201cfloral notes\u201d types, the coffee club regularly gathers to test out new gourmet brews.<\/p>\n<p>Throw in some company-wide potlucks and catered team meetings or lunches and RL Solutions has this whole food and drink thing nailed down\u2014not to mention that if someone is feeling up to it, they can hop on a ferry and enjoy a scenic picnic lunch on Toronto Island in less than 20 minutes. It&#8217;s starting to make sense that even RL Solutions&#8217; office location ties into that &#8220;get away from the city&#8221; motif.<\/p>\n<h3>Culture<\/h3>\n<p>The unofficial motto at RL Solutions is \u201cgood people do great things,\u201d and that\u2019s led Malaviya and co. to craft a passionate and dedicated team of professionals. Even if every employee were to switch to making canoes tomorrow, they would be able to excel at it, simply because it\u2019s the right group of people all working hard together.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106328\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-11.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-11\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-11.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-11-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-11-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-11-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-11-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>That canoe idea led to the creation of the storied Canoe Club, a recognition for RL Solutions employees who have been with the company for over 10 years. That\u2019s not the only club though\u2014maybe you want to try your hand and join the anime, music, bead, salad or chess club? The good thing is that none of those require 10 years of service, though you might need that equivalent in experience to beat some of RL Solutions\u2019 best chess players.<\/p>\n<blockquote><p>&#8220;If you hire the right people, you trust them to do the right thing\u2014and it\u2019s in this spirit that we built our space the way we did.\u201c<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<p>There\u2019s ping pong too, but not like usual. RL Solutions has a stadium, complete with a wallpapered audience. The annual tournament draws in almost every employee and their family, and it\u2019s no holds barred\u2014champions care not for community when it comes to the storied halls of the ping pong stadium.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_106309\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-106309\" style=\"width: 1550px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-106309 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-30.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-30\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-30.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-30-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-30-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-30-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095522\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-30-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-106309\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The crowd on the left side of the room cheers these ping-pongers on.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>If ping pong isn\u2019t the preferred workout, there\u2019s a complete gym on-site with showers, along with a wellness room. For those who want to take the workout beyond the in-house gym, RL Solutions offers a fitness reimbursement.<\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106314\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-25.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-25\" width=\"1549\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-25.jpg 1549w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-25-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-25-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-25-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-25-1280x854.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1549px) 100vw, 1549px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106313\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-26.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-26\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstatio