 \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106320\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-19.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-19\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-19.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-19-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-19-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-19-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-19-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106321\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-18.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-18\" width=\"1549\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-18.jpg 1549w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-18-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-18-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-18-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095520\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-18-1280x854.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1549px) 100vw, 1549px\" \/><\/p>\n<h3>Education<\/h3>\n<p>RL Solutions keep employees well-fed and physically fit, so naturally, education is imperative as well. The company offers employees an educational assistance program to work on outside of the office and other non-linear ways to keep the team growing in the right direction.<\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_106334\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-106334\" style=\"width: 1550px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img class=\"wp-image-106334 size-full\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095517\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-5-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-106334\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Faux movie posters dot the office, representing RL Solutions\u2019 different teams.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106329\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-10.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-10\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-10.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-10-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-10-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-10-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-10-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-106330\" src=\"https:\/\/localhost:8080\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-9.jpg\" alt=\"RL Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-9\" width=\"1550\" height=\"1033\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-9.jpg 1550w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-9-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-9-1024x682.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/wpassets.brainstation.io\/app\/uploads\/2018\/07\/13095518\/RL-Solutions-Office-Toronto-KillerSpaces-Techvibes-9-1280x853.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1550px) 100vw, 1550px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>There are continuing education courses and maker-space projects, along with lunch and learns led by both employees and outside experts. Some of the clubs are also focused on improving life skills, such as the Toastmasters club that helps employees get better at public speaking.<\/p>\n<h6 style=\"text-align: right;\">Photos by Matt Odynski<\/h6>\n<p>Do you have an amazing office and would like to be featured here? Get in touch with us:\u00a0<a href=\"http:\/\/killerspaces@techvibes.com\/\">killerspaces@techvibes.com<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>At one point, RL Solutions\u2019 software fit on three floppy disks. Things are a bit different now. The healthcare enterprise software company, founded in 1997 (back when floppy disks made sense) has expanded just a bit from those early days.\u00a0RL Solutions now works with over 2,000 clients around the world, including SickKids and Johns Hopkins. &hellip; <a href=\"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/magazine\/killer-spaces-rl-solutions-toronto\">Continued<\/a><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":76244,"featured_media":106333,"menu_order":0,"template":"","meta":[],"categories":[13],"tags":[20,3079],"magazine-series":[48],"magazine-region":[427],"magazine-topic":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/wp\/api\/wp\/v2\/magazine\/105450"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/wp\/api\/wp\/v2\/magazine"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/wp\/api\/wp\/v2\/types\/magazine"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/wp\/api\/wp\/v2\/users\/76244"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/wp\/api\/wp\/v2\/magazine\/105450\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/wp\/api\/wp\/v2\/media\/106333"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/wp\/api\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=105450"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/wp\/api\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=105450"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/brainstation.io\/wp\/api\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=105450"},{"taxonomy":"magazine-series","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/brai